40625022@unknown@formal@none@1@S@It has lost its ground of being and floats in a mist of appearances.@@@@1@14@@oe@1-12-2014
40625023@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Relativism and equality are its characteristic diseases.@@@@1@7@@oe@1-12-2014
