40625048@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Thus with regard to the loss of tradition, in the change from order to disorder the metaphysics of change works itself out as a disruption of the individual soul, a change in which man continues as an objective ontological existent, but no longer as a man.@@@@1@46@@oe@1-12-2014
